27319.title: Illustration for 'Whatever the Weather May Be', Riley Songs of Cheer

extended_text.content:
Working from his studio in Brown County, Indiana, Vawter drew upon real life for the characters that Riley described.

Songs of Cheer is a collection of poems of gladness, content and consolation.

Vawter illustrated fourteen books by Indiana poet James Whitcomb Riley.
